<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hasty" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hasty,</orth> 1) quick, speedy: <cit><quote>upon h. employment,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.139" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 139</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h. powder,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 1, 64</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a h. spark,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our h. sending,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 4</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) in haste, having no time to lose: <cit><quote>are you so h.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 49</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.61" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 5, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.162" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 162</bibl>.
<lb />3) rash, inconsiderate, passionate: <bibl n="shak. luc 49" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.169" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.3.97" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 3, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.19" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.2" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.261" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 261</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.7.32" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 178</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 168</bibl>.
<lb />Adverbially: <cit><quote>spoke in choler, ill and h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 1, 34</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>